comment_regular_data.body:
Didn't manage to find any other fix than the one you just pushed, however I noticed that `UIEnter` is still triggered with channel ID 1 when attaching a UI on the listening channel. So the `CHAN_STDIO` here needs change:
```c
  if (use_remote_ui) {
    do_autocmd_uienter(CHAN_STDIO, true);
    TIME_MSG("UIEnter autocommands");
  }
```

